# =============================================================================
# 🔐 SECRETS & CREDENTIALS (zero tolerance — never commit these)
# =============================================================================

# Cryptographic keys & certificates
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
*.crt
*.cer
*.csr
id_rsa
id_rsa.*
id_ed25519
