# Netrc (FTP/HTTP basic auth)
.netrc
.netrc.*

# Cloud provider credentials (Google, AWS, Azure, etc.)
**/.aws/
**/.aws/**
aws-credentials
credentials
**/.config/gcloud/
**/.config/gcloud/**
